  "text": "Contrarily, sub-text level detection methods [CITATION_1] , [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] , [CITATION_4] , [CITATION_5] , [CITATION_6] , [CITATION_7] [CITATION_8] , [CITATION_9] , [CITATION_10] , [CITATION_11] , [CITATION_12] [CITATION_13] , [CITATION_14] , [CITATION_15] only predicts parts that are combined to make a text instance. Such sub-text mainly includes pixel-level and components-level.",
